Story: public access to merbcasts site

  As an anonymous visitor
  I want to come to the site and see merbcasts
  So that I can be awesome with Merb

  Scenario: visit home page
    Given an anonymous user
    When the user visits /
    Then the visitor should see the page: Casts index
    And the page should have the heading: Merbcasts
  
  Scenario: visit the merbcasts index
    Given an anonymous user
    When the user visits /casts
    Then the visitor should see the page: Casts index

